1
00:00:37,799 --> 00:00:38,640
Uncle Sheng.

2
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:40,359
I'm begging you, you have to help me.

3
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,600
Get Liu Li out of Benevolence Hospital.

4
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,119
It must have been her.

5
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,759
She must be the one who hurt my dad.

6
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,799
Uncle Sheng.

7
00:00:50,479 --> 00:00:52,079
You're a Benevolence Hospital shareholder.

8
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:53,759
Your words carry a lot of weight.

9
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,759
If you're willing to step in,

10
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:58,159
you can veto Jiang Min's appointment.

11
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,479
Siqi...

12
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,759
I'm sorry about what happened to your dad.

13
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:05,000
I also hope he gets better soon.

14
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,519
But as for the hospital,

15
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,200
I don't want to interfere too much.

16
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,879
To be honest with you,

17
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,719
I've looked over Jiang Min's resume.

18
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,680
He's not from the medical field,

19
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,280
but his track record is impressive.

20
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,680
He graduated from a top school,

21
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:19,239
and has pulled off many M&A deals.

22
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:21,040
I think he's talented.

23
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,120
So regarding his appointment as

24
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:25,159
Benevolence Hospital's Administrative Dean,

25
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:27,159
I don't have any objections.

26
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,239
But...

27
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,040
But this is obviously Liu Li's doing!

28
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,719
She's using my dad's critical condition

29
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,319
to swallow up my family's assets.

30
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,799
Uncle Sheng...

31
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,680
For the sake of your friendship

32
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,200
with my dad after all these years,

33
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,400
please help me.

34
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,079
Help my dad hold on to the hospital.

35
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,680
Siqi, you're still young.

36
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:47,480
You're too idealistic.

37
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,280
Running a hospital is still a business.

38
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,640
Profit is the goal.

39
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,879
As for your family's personal matters,

40
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,640
as long as they don't affect business,

41
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,200
I don't need to get involved.

42
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:58,799
I can't help you with this.

43
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,759
All right, Uncle Sheng.

44
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,680
Then...

45
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,599
I'll get going.

46
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,120
Okay. Be careful on the way.

47
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,000
Goodbye.

48
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:41,639
You heard all that, right?

49
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,120
Thanks for your strong support, Mr. Sheng.

50
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,080
I hope you'll keep your word too.

51
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,560
My lips are sealed.

52
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,840
Help me take over Benevolence Hospital,

53
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,000
and about that matter,

54
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,120
I won't say a single word.

55
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,719
Did you find it?

56
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:22,439
Did you find the original video?

57
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,199
I've turned the whole house upside down.

58
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:25,680
But I still haven't found it.

59
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,520
Keep looking.

60
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,039
If you find any clues,

61
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,039
contact me anytime.

62
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,439
Don't worry, Chairman Sheng.

63
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:33,599
We're in the same boat.

64
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,479
I only need people who are valuable.

65
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,199
Prove your worth.

66
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,520
Chairman Sheng...

67
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,039
Haven't I proven it

68
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,159
enough already?

69
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:53,120
If Sheng Yuanzhou breaks the engagement,

70
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,360
don't blame me for being ruthless.

71
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,599
A forced marriage never works.

72
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,879
Siqi doesn't want to marry into my family.

73
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,400
Why are you still pushing it?

74
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,520
She's just a kid. She doesn't understand.

75
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,400
But we had an agreement.

76
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,840
Siqi and Yuanzhou are engaged!

77
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:11,960
Agreement?

78
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:15,240
That agreement was only for back then.

79
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,279
More than ten years have passed.

80
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,720
What do I have to fear from you now?

81
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:19,800
Fine.

82
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,639
You're really not afraid

83
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,839
I'll expose that Bai Zimei wasn't crazy?

84
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,879
Do you have proof?

85
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,079
Proof?

86
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,519
All right.

87
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,319
I figured as much.

88
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:37,040
Here's video of Bai Zimei before she died.

89
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,560
You can take it back and watch it.

90
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:42,240
In this footage,

91
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
Bai Zimei speaks clearly,

92
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,600
with sound logic,

93
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,480
and she shows no signs of mental illness.

94
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,920
Plus my testimony as her attending doctor.

95
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:50,879
Think you can deny it?

96
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,560
Just as I thought.

97
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,480
You really did hold something back.

98
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,680
But if you come forward to confirm it,

99
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,800
you'll drag yourself down too.

100
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,560
For your daughter's marriage,

101
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,240
do you think it's worth it?

102
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,399
For my daughter,

103
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,360
there's nothing I won't do.

104
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:11,439
If Siqi marries into the Sheng family,

105
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,759
I'll hand over the original video to you.

106
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:14,639
And on top of that,

107
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,560
I want shares of Prosperity Group

108
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,319
given to Siqi.

109
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,439
At least five percent.

110
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:23,240
You've got some nerve.

111
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:25,160
Compared to having your reputation ruined,

112
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,680
and being investigated by the police,

113
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,199
this is nothing, is it?

114
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,199
All right, I've said what I needed to say.

115
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,240
Now it's up to you.

116
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,879
Are you threatening me?

117
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:39,879
Afraid Benevolence Hospital will go under?

118
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,480
Or that I'll crush Lin Siqi?

119
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,879
If you dare, we can perish together.

120
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,560
You'll lose far more than I will.

121
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,800
I didn't get where I am today

122
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,959
by being afraid of threats.

123
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,639
Fine. We'll see about that.

124
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,360
Before you headed out,

125
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,279
did you take your meds?

126
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,720
Sheng Shizhong!

127
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,560
I'm warning you for the last time.

128
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,879
Honey, don't be angry.

129
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:10,879
You already have a weak heart.

130
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:12,000
Take your medicine first.

131
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,160
I'm going out for a bit.

132
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:27,160
You...

133
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,759
Liu Li!

134
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,800
Don't forget,

135
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:36,079
I'm the one who set you two up.

136
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,199
You...

137
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,519
You're murdering me!

138
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,120
Don't be so dramatic.

139
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,319
I'm just looking out for you.

140
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,959
So I had her give you some extra vitamins.

141
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,199
Sheng Shizhong!

142
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,279
I'll kill...

143
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,480
Let me do it.

144
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:42,639
Where are you going with a suitcase?

145
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:47,079
To the hospital to stay with my dad.

146
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,120
You packed so much.

147
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,519
Is Uncle's condition that serious?

148
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,319
My dad's in the hospital right now,

149
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,920
still in a coma.

150
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,279
Auntie Li, she...

151
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,319
She not only betrayed my dad,

152
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:05,240
now she even wants to take the hospital.

153
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:27,439
Xiaobei, my head's a mess right now.

154
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,920
all I can think about is finding a way

155
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:33,000
to help my dad protect his life's work,

156
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,279
but I have no idea what to do.

157
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,720
It'll be okay.

158
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:37,639
You still have me.

159
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,559
We'll figure something out.

160
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,279
Hello.

161
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,039
I just want to say a few words.

162
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,159
It'll only take a few minutes.

163
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,240
Sorry, Mr. Yang isn't home.

164
00:08:58,879 --> 00:08:59,960
What is that supposed to mean?

165
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,320
His car just drove in.

166
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:02,399
He's obviously at home.

167
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,080
He just doesn't want to see me.

168
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,720
It's fine. Next.

169
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:15,159
Uncle Li, Uncle Li!

170
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:17,399
Uncle Li!

171
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,559
Just help me this once, okay?

172
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:21,080
It's not that I don't want to help you,

173
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:23,200
but my hands are tied.

174
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,320
Mr. Li!

175
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,200
As far as I know, you have a daughter too.

176
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,000
If your daughter were like Siqi,

177
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,919
begging for help to protect your assets,

178
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,200
it would break your heart, wouldn't it?

179
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:34,120
For my old friendship with your father,

180
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:35,639
I'll help you this once.

181
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,639
Thank you, thank you, Uncle Li!

182
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,679
Thank you.

183
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:46,799
Well? There's finally some hope.

184
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,200
As everyone knows,

185
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,360
Dean Lin is hospitalized in a coma.

186
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,840
And me,

187
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,799
I have no management experience at all.

188
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,399
But a hospital as big as ours

189
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,480
still needs to keep operating.

190
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:07,399
So,

191
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:09,759
I've invited a seasoned management expert

192
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:11,440
to take over for Dean Lin,

193
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,600
and run Benevolence Hospital.

194
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,399
Now,

195
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,799
let me introduce him to you all.

196
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:17,399
A top graduate from Massachusetts,

197
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,480
Mr. Jiang Min.

198
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:19,440
Please welcome him.

199
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,200
Thank you for your trust, Ms. Liu Li.

200
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,120
I'll do everything I can

201
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,000
to elevate Benevolence Hospital.

202
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,399
I disagree.

203
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,000
I believe every shareholder

204
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,279
will have their own judgment.

205
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,080
I demand a Vote.

206
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,320
Fine. I respect your opinion.

207
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,840
Then let's have everyone vote.

208
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,879
Uncle Li.

209
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:18,879
Mr. Wang...

210
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,240
Didn't we agree...

211
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,480
Then I'll continue.

212
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,279
As for me,

213
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,360
I don't like empty talk.

214
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,080
So let me show everyone

215
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,759
my future plan for Benevolence Hospital.

216
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:32,919
Please take a look.

217
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:49,519
What is this?

218
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,000
What the hell is this?

219
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,799
I have no idea.

220
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,919
Over half the board has already agreed

221
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:06,919
to block Jiang Min.

222
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:15,200
You used to run a company.

223
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,240
Me?

224
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,279
Don't you know by now?

225
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:18,919
Not a single word they say is true.

226
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,960
So what if you ran a company?

227
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,519
Integrity is what matters most.

228
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,639
They're all such big-shot leaders.

229
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:24,360
You think they would lie to me?

230
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:26,960
You can wait and see.

231
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:28,360
Then

232
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,519
what do you suggest?

233
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:32,720
I actually have something here

234
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:34,480
that you might need.

235
00:12:39,559 --> 00:12:40,559
I believe everyone

236
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,600
has seen these photos already.

237
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,759
Given Liu Li and Jiang Min's

238
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:45,840
improper relationship,

239
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:46,879
I propose

240
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:49,679
removing Jiang Min as acting dean.

241
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,759
Ms. Lin, you really came prepared.

242
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,960
As for my relationship with Ms. Liu Li,

243
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,960
I won't overexplain.

244
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:07,879
You're free to think whatever you want.

245
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,200
But what I will say is,

246
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,960
Benevolence Hospital hired me

247
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,159
not to judge the Lin family's affairs.

248
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,600
I'm here to make everyone money.

249
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,200
Come in.

250
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,000
What you are holding right now

251
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,159
is a custom Benevolence Hospital

252
00:13:34,159 --> 00:13:35,399
business transformation plan.

253
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,399
The first step

254
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:40,080
is targeting the Premium market

255
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,720
and building up VIP services.

256
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,919
Cancel the old cancer center plan,

257
00:13:44,399 --> 00:13:47,120
and convert it strictly for

258
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,080
a VIP Premium medical tower.

259
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:49,840
You can't do that!

260
00:13:50,639 --> 00:13:52,399
Healthcare should serve the public,

261
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:53,919
not just the premium crowd.

262
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,039
Young lady,

263
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,200
a hospital is a business too,

264
00:13:58,519 --> 00:13:59,639
not a charity.

265
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:01,679
We have to answer to shareholder interests.

266
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,720
But that betrays a healer's compassion.

267
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:04,360
Alright.

268
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:06,480
Let the shareholders decide by Vote.

269
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,519
If the shareholders don't approve my plan,

270
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:10,080
you can dismiss me on the spot.

271
00:14:10,879 --> 00:14:11,320
How about it?

272
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,200
Fine.

273
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,559
Then I'll ask everyone

274
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,039
to vote by a show of hands.

275
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,799
Please raise your hand to support my plan.

276
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,000
Agreed.

277
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:44,919
Passed unanimously.

278
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,919
Well, Ms. Lin?

279
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:49,840
Anything else you want to say?

280
00:14:59,679 --> 00:15:00,279
Siqi.

281
00:15:01,039 --> 00:15:01,720
Don't lose heart.

282
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,360
We'll figure something out.

283
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:06,600
I will never

284
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,919
let them steal my dad's hospital.

